```
$ rackabel deploy --dry-run --user-library lib
User Library: lib ([..])
planned deploy (nothing was changed):
  - slug: [..]
  - target: [..]Extensions[..]
  - build if stale, then copy:
      [..]manifest.json -> [..]Extensions[..]manifest.json
      [..]dist/extension.js -> [..]Extensions[..]dist/extension.js

```

Undo when nothing is deployed is a clean no-op, not an error:

```
$ rackabel deploy --undo --user-library lib
User Library: lib ([..])
[✓] nothing to undo — [..] is not deployed

```
